Taya Straton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taya_Straton 0 Taya Straton (27 November 1960 – 26 February 1996) was an Australian actress, who remains best known for playing "Spider" Simpson during the final year of Prisoner in 1986. She committed suicide in 1996.
